{"tid":362752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國22歲女天生沒陰道 上網募款「想試試做愛的滋味」","createTime":"2017-08-17T07:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T17:46:22.000Z","uid":75969,"like":225,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eab698d859c1ffead9db5227aac4457d7d8d543e","tid":362752,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpcryfyn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpcryfyn.jpg&h=04abfcf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">茉絲罹患罕病「苗勒管發育不全綜合症」，造成先天性子宮喪失，子宮頸及陰道上部發育不全。（擷取自YouTube）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國亞利桑那州22歲女子茉絲（Kaylee Moats），因患有罕見疾病「苗勒管發育不全綜合症（MRKH）」，讓她不能像正常女性一樣擁有子宮、陰道等性器官，令她未曾享受過魚水之歡。為實現「夢想」，茉絲近日在網路上發起募款，希望能籌措足額手術費建造人工陰道。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，茉絲是一名平面設計師，從未經歷過月經的她，18歲那年在母親陪同下到醫院檢查，這才發現罹患了罕病「苗勒管發育不全綜合症」，這種先天性畸形導致茉絲生下來就沒有子宮，也造成她子宮頸及陰道上部發育不全，在本應是陰道口的地方，更只有淺淺的凹陷，讓她不僅無法懷孕，連正常的性愛都無法擁有。<br />\n<br />\n醫生宣布了壞消息後，茉絲隨即陷入困惑與低潮，同時她也擔心與男朋友的感情是否將因此改變。花了將近一個月的時間，茉絲最終鼓起勇氣向對方坦白，所幸男朋友展現了十足的支持，表示願意陪她度過這一切。<br />\n<br />\n不過，雖然男友已明言不介意，茉絲仍希望接受手術，打造一個人工陰道。茉絲目前在募資網站上的募款目標是1.5萬美元（約為新台幣45萬元），「縱使這一切將會很疼痛」茉絲說，「我還是想跟男友做愛，這將讓我變成一個完整的女人」。<br />\n<br />\n苗勒管發育不全的患者具有第二性徵，其中包括乳房發育及陰毛等外觀性徵，患者卵巢完整，排卵功能正常，所以雖因不具有子宮而無法懷孕，患者還是能透過體外受精及代孕等方式擁有自己親生的孩子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxUJNXdCNGE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkxUJNXdCNGE&d=lfE49gnlDj4OFRuwGkcSdTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1cca8cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxUJNXdCNGE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2164412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2164412&d=lfE49gnlDj4OFRuwGkcSdTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a916e113\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2164412&h=a32da89b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2164412</a>"},{"pid":"ae938f44c5d693dd4469a5f089f06683b66704b8","tid":362752,"uid":65429,"like":73,"dislike":3,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"哇, 冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a29c4d1e82aea381a10ab0a2cd8bb2f4ff7fd0f","tid":362752,"uid":55458,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b51db96eaa976fb3f89c6a976700f04b674251","tid":362752,"uid":18845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0c8b8af0f98f7a1b24031977f6f7f86e9ce87a","tid":362752,"uid":132557,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"資助你造愛  有無得睇LIVE先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e522b4205e18433413535f32a299aed9075fc35f","tid":362752,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"條仔幾叻，記者黎到扮唔知"},{"pid":"d9cdfb1f4c2a4354e8c3d15fbb4e9f78310fcfea","tid":362752,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199537d0903d90c340911943ee78f60fd3ec05d1","tid":362752,"uid":39628,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"你捐錢, 但係無份做<img src=\"/